INTRO                                             You see a beautiful and magestic lady seated on a log throne. She looks up at   you with a big smile. "Guildmaster! I heard thee were here! Welcome!"                                                   NAME                                              "I am Queen Melissa, of the SIRENS."                                                                                                                                                                    JOB                                               "I rule the SIRENS who liveth here."                                                                                                                                                                    BYE                                               "Fare well, heroic one! It is always a joy to speak with thee!"                                                                                                                                                                                           "Oh my, how I wish I could answer that!"                                                                                                                                                                SIRENS                                            "Yes. Legend says when we sing, men turn to stone." She starts singing. "As you can see, it art but a terrible MYTH."                                                                                   MYTH                                              "Ah, well. Anyway, we are related to the MERMAID race. "Tis why we like to be   near water."                                                                                                            MERMAID                                           "Yes, we love to swim. As thou visit here, be sure to visit Losi and Neela.     They canst help thee with a ranged weapon. Don't forget the FRUIT!"                                                     FRUIT                                             "Thou may use the banban trees for fruit, anytime thou wish. And now, I wish    to bestoeth my BLESSING on thee, that thou may hath luck on thy quest."                                                 BLESSING                                          Melissa leans gently forward, and gives you a big kiss, then says no more.                                                                                                                              